headline: NVIDIA ascends to Aa1 status at Moody’s on AI infrastructure dominance
summary: Investing.com -- Moody’s Ratings has elevated NVIDIA Corporation’s (NASDAQ:NVDA) senior unsecured rating to Aa1, marking a significant milestone in the chipmaker’s financial evolution. The credit agency simultaneously maintained a positive outlook, suggesting further upward mobility is possible as the firm solidifies its grip on the artificial intelligence sector.
